    "description": "如果你喜欢它，请务必添加至愿望清单，并让我们知道你的感受!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022970/extras/faf70d7776a02a5985188e3a6fbc7fb7.webp?t=1737393881\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br>《黯淡之森》是一个极具挑战性的类 Rogue 快节奏回合制 RPG。<br><br>在这个基于回合制的战斗游戏中，你需要指挥冒险者小队，并在游戏中体验到肉鸽和能力构筑的元素！<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>不一样的回合制战斗模式：半自动的回合制战斗给你带来不一样的游戏体验</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022970/extras/fb22faa746fbbfe46524ac08eefc1fad.poster.avif?t=1737393881\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022970/extras/fb22faa746fbbfe46524ac08eefc1fad.webm?t=1737393881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022970/extras/fb22faa746fbbfe46524ac08eefc1fad.mp4?t=1737393881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>建造你的营地，吸引更多能力独特的伙伴加入你</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022970/extras/cd6d085e6df41d8a44651959ad53163c.poster.avif?t=1737393881\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022970/extras/cd6d085e6df41d8a44651959ad53163c.webm?t=1737393881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022970/extras/cd6d085e6df41d8a44651959ad53163c.mp4?t=1737393881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>死亡不是结束，而是你走向高手旅程的开始。随着你游戏的继续，你将解锁新的角色、攻击、技能和更多游戏内容</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在面对最终之前，努力获得新的卡片提升冒险者的能力！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022970/extras/2ff75e31a41c0a4134d832460869d12d.poster.avif?t=1737393881\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022970/extras/2ff75e31a41c0a4134d832460869d12d.webm?t=1737393881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022970/extras/2ff75e31a41c0a4134d832460869d12d.mp4?t=1737393881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>来体验独特的像素风格吧！</li></ul><br>你能找到森林腐化的真相并拯救森林吗？<br><br>冒险前进吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022970/extras/54929c6e3a2465cda265fdd68d4de867.poster.avif?t=1737393881\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022970/extras/54929c6e3a2465cda265fdd68d4de867.webm?t=1737393881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022970/extras/54929c6e3a2465cda265fdd68d4de867.mp4?t=1737393881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
